See directories
	/sps/ilm/allouche/MySoftwares/NNMP-STM-11-Code         =================> IN2P3
	/home/allouche/MySoftwares/NNMP-STM-11-Code            =================> Local
	/sto2/ssd/allouche/MySoftwares/NNMP-STM-11-Code   =================> Lynx

make : 
	source /sps/ilm/allouche/MySoftwares/NNMP-STM-11-Code/env.sh       ===============> IN2P3
	source /home/allouche/MySoftwares/NNMP-STM-11-Code/env.sh          ===============> Local
	source /sto2/ssd/allouche/MySoftwares/NNMP-STM-11-Code/env.sh ==================> Lynx

to use them

submitNNMP_CPU => submit CPU job using input file. Type submitNNMP_CPU to show options
submitNNMP_GPU => submit GPU job using input file. Type submitNNMP_GPU to show options

xbuildData   => build data in interactive  (use srunInteactiveCPU or srunInteactiveGPU before)
xevaluationEnsemble => make an evalution. xevaluationEnsemble in interactive. subGPU xevaluationEnsemble to run on batch (see also submitNNMP_GPU&submitNNMP_CPU)
xpredict	=> make an prediction. xpredict in interactive. subGPU xpredict to run on batch (use instead submitNNMP_GPU&submitNNMP_CPU)
xtrain	=> make an train. xtrain in interactive. subGPU xtrain to run on batch (use instead submitNNMP_GPU&submitNNMP_CPU)

subGPU => submit a script (xtrain, xpredict, xevaluationEnsemble, xbuildData) on GPU
srunInteactiveCPU => to obtain a interactive CPU machine
srunInteactiveGPU =>  to obtain a interactive GPU machine

## Scripts (bash)
### scriptsLocal all bash scripts for a local machine (specially if you have a GPU).
### scriptsLynx all bash scripts for the cluster lynx.
### scriptsIN2P3 all bash scripts for the IN2P2 calculation center.

## Main programs
### buildData.py. 
	see xbuildData script : from csv& png of Pierre => database for the training program

### train.py : using the database created by buildData.py, make the training. See traing.inp & xtrain
               ./xtrain to run in interactive. submitNNMP_CPU or submitNNMP_GPU(in2p3 only) to submit the job
		type submitNNMP_CPU or submitNNMP_GPU without parameters to show all options

### evaluation.py : test the models (one or anensemble of models) using a database
               ./xevaluation to run in interactive. submitNNMP_CPU or submitNNMP_GPU(in2p3 only) to submit the job
### predict.py : predict the STM image using a POSCAR file
               ./xpredict to run in interactive. submitNNMP_CPU or submitNNMP_GPU(in2p3 only) to submit the job

## Example : see example directory

## Warnning : If you change the directory of the code, go to scripts* directory and type ./xchdirCode
